Package pec

Interface IEvent

All Known Implementing Classes:
AntMoveEvent, EvaporationEvent, Event, SimulationReportEvent
public interface IEvent
The IEvent interface defines the contract for an event in the simulation. It provides methods for setting/getting event time, event type, and executing the event.
